<div id="topleft"><br />Because BYU-Idaho is committed to providing you with an innovative educational experience, the university has built greater flexibility and versatility into your degree options.<br /><br /><span class="italics"><span class="italics"> BYU-Idaho has four bachelor's degree structures designed to help you:<br /><br /></span></span>
<ul>
<li>Have flexibility</li>
<li>Graduate faster</li>
<li>Save money</li>
<li>Prepare for a career and life options</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div id="topright"><img alt="Flexible Degrees Image" src="http://www.byui.edu/Images/Academic-Advising/flexible-degrees-text.gif" /></div>
